'''Georges Pottier''' was a [[sailor]] from [[France]],<ref name="A" /> who represented his country at the [[Sailing at the 1900 Summer Olympics – .5 to 1 ton|1900 Summer Olympics]] in [[Meulan]], [[France]]. Georges Pottier as crew, was disqualified in first race of the [[Ton class|0.5 to 1 ton]] and did not finished in the second race. He did this with the boat ''Sidi-Fekkar''.

